==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Revoluble
<hw>Rev"o*lu*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>revolubilis</ets> that may be rolled back. See
<er>Revolve</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable of revolving; rotatory;
revolving.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Us, then, to whom the thrice three year⟦br⟧
Hath filled his <qex>revoluble</qex> orb since our arrival here,⟦br⟧
I blame not.</q> <rj><qau>Chapman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Revolute</ent>⟦br⟧
